1
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:54,960
Ling'er.

2
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:56,000
Ling'er.

3
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,760
Ling'er.

4
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:01,160
Ling'er.

5
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:03,600
Get away.

6
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:06,800
Yunyuan.

7
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:07,800
Calm down.

8
00:01:08,039 --> 00:01:08,970
Ling'er is fine.

9
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,080
Is he suffering from Qi deviation?

10
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,760
These two are in the way.

11
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,080
She is fine.

12
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,090
Is Ling'er really okay?

13
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:18,880
But...

14
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,090
Why hasn't she woken up yet?

15
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,210
Ling'er.

16
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:23,400
Yunyuan.

17
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,780
Let's take Ling'er back first, okay?

18
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:29,720
Okay.

19
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,810
We'll take Ling'er back first.

20
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,080
She's just asleep.

21
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,000
She'll be fine once she wakes up.

22
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,530
Ling'er.

23
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,810
Let's go back first.

24
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,050
Let's go back first.

25
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,930
What is going on?

26
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,360
Could Yunyuan have been corrupted by demonic energy long ago?

27
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:50,620
And he usually suppresses his demonic nature with reason?

28
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:53,039
No.

29
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:55,600
I need to go back and question Qingluan and Yueying.

30
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,460
Brother Di Yun.

31
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,060
Brother Di Yun.

32
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,900
It's a good thing you came.

33
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,360
Why did you let her act so recklessly?

34
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:04,200
Sister Ling'er's cultivation is higher than mine.

35
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,640
I couldn't stop her.

36
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,920
That's why I left you a letter.

37
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,449
I'll deal with you when we get back.

38
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:24,690
Shihun pays respects to the Grand Protector.

39
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,960
Did you get the Spirit Pearl?

40
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,760
Reporting to the Grand Protector.

41
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,320
I did see the Spirit Pearl.

42
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,160
But I didn't retrieve it.

43
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,360
Useless thing.

44
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,040
When I saw the Dragon Princess summon the Spirit Pearl,

45
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,900
I intended to snatch it and leave.

46
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:41,360
But...

47
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:44,920
I discovered there seemed to be a problem with the Spirit Pearl.

48
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:46,920
Are you sure it was the Spirit Pearl?

49
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,800
I am certain.

50
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,360
But for some reason,

51
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,800
the Spirit Pearl had no Soul.

52
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,880
The priority now

53
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,810
is to find the Spirit Pearl's Soul.

54
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,840
I beg the Grand Protector

55
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,170
to give me a chance to atone for my failure.

56
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:01,320
Go back and continue investigating the whereabouts of the Soul.

57
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,760
When the time is right,

58
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:06,200
bring both the Spirit Pearl and the Soul back.

59
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,620
As you command.

60
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,440
Lisha.

61
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:15,880
My Lord.

62
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:16,960
It seems

63
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,760
the position of Grand Protector

64
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,560
needs a new occupant.

65
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,560
Please appease your anger, my Lord.

66
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,200
Once I retrieve those items,

67
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,760
you will be able to return to the Three Realms.

68
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:29,640
And make the whole world tremble.

69
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,000
Do not make me wait too long.

70
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,490
I will not fail your guidance, my Lord.

71
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:39,360
Once my Primordial Spirit is restored,

72
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,720
I will make all living things

73
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,920
crawl at my feet

74
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,090
struggling for their pathetic lives.

75
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:48,480
I await your return, my Lord.

76
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,560
Qingluan.

77
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:56,520
Have you noticed

78
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,440
anything wrong with your sworn brother lately?

79
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,240
No.

80
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:03,210
But he seems to show signs of being corrupted by demonic energy.

81
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,360
My sworn brother uses himself as a conduit,

82
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,040
and the Qiankun Cauldron as a furnace

83
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:10,120
to refine the hostile energy of Kunmi for a thousand years.

84
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,600
He has never made a mistake.

85
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,960
Perhaps he has been busy lately

86
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,290
and hasn't cultivated.

87
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,560
He just needs a few days of seclusion.

88
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:20,120
So that is how he purifies the demonic energy of Kunmi.

89
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,160
Such merit...

90
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,640
I cannot compare.

91
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:24,760
But if he does this,

92
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,080
will it hurt Ling'er?

93
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,960
You can rest assured.

94
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,520
Even if my sworn brother hurts himself,

95
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,080
he would never hurt Ling'er.

96
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,760
He cares for the people of Kunmi,

97
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,720
but Ling'er

98
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:36,170
is the most important person in his heart.

99
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,040
No.

100
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,400
I am still worried.

101
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,960
I want to take her to my place to recover.

102
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:40,560
Hey.

103
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,760
If you take Ling'er away,

104
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,320
my sworn brother will go mad.

105
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:43,800
Then,

106
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,460
how about this.

107
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,320
I will leave this Sound Transmission Stone with you.

108
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,120
When Ling'er wakes up,

109
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,920
give it to her

110
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,920
and have her contact me.

111
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,850
Is that alright?

112
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,400
Okay.

113
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,240
The King of Kunmi is watching too closely.

114
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,440
I must think of a way.

115
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,560
Sister,

116
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,760
don't you think the King of Kunmi

117
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,120
seems very idle lately?

118
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,400
He does seem quite idle lately.

119
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,200
Sister,

120
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,760
look at the King of Kunmi.

121
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,360
His look is so fierce.

122
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,640
I'm scared.

123
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,160
Oh, don't be scared.

124
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,080
Yunyuan.

125
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,560
Ling'er.

126
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,360
Are you feeling better today?

127
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,640
My injuries are fully healed.

128
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:34,300
Look, if you don't believe me.

129
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:37,760
Yunyuan,

130
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,600
I want to go out for a walk.

131
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,720
May I?

132
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,600
No.

133
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,440
You have just recovered.

134
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,900
It is not safe outside.

135
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,890
You are not allowed to go anywhere.

136
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,120
Fine, I won't go then.

137
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,560
Yinfeng,

138
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,960
come back to the room with me.

139
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,760
Yes, Sister.

140
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,040
Ever since I was injured,

141
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,960
Yunyuan hasn't let me go out.

142
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:10,290
He even set up a barrier at Cloud Recesses.

143
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,760
I can't go anywhere.

144
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,290
It really makes me so angry.

145
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,360
Sister,

146
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,340
don't be angry.

147
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,320
The King of Kunmi is just trying to protect you.

148
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,160
How about

149
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,480
you try my newly brewed Nectar Wine?

150
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,480
This wine

151
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,760
is very fragrant.

152
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,250
It has the scent of several flowers

153
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,560
and tastes sweet.

154
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,360
Your skills are really good.

155
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,320
I'm glad you like it, Sister.

156
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,480
Have another cup.

157
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:46,880
Okay.

158
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,080
Sister,

159
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,810
this is wine, after all.

160
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,159
Don't drink too much.

161
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,000
Here.

162
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,560
By the way,

163
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,240
Sister,

164
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,640
do you still want to go out for a walk?

165
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:05,880
Of course I do.

166
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,160
I'm bored to death here.

167
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,360
Do you have a way to get out?

168
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,520
I...

169
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,640
That might not be a good idea.

170
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,800
So you do.

171
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,600
Tell me.

172
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:24,840
If you don't tell me, I won't let you tag along anymore.

173
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,560
Fine, I'll tell you.

174
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,640
Listen.

175
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:35,040
King Kunmi isn't always at the Cloud Recesses.

176
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:38,200
Why don't we sneak out while he's away?

177
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,200
You can take your Spirit Bead,

178
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,800
smash the barrier,

179
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,760
and then we can get out.

180
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,520
I don't know if that will work.

181
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:51,480
I always feel that using the Spirit Bead

182
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,300
doesn't feel quite right.

183
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,560
It feels like something is missing.

184
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,200
Sister,

185
00:07:57,360 --> 00:08:00,640
since you feel the Spirit Bead is missing something,

186
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,720
why don't you ask someone?

187
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,360
Who would I ask?

188
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:06,180
I can't even leave this place.

189
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,920
Why don't we ask King Kunmi?

190
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,560
He is all-powerful.

191
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:15,160
He must know something.

192
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,020
I don't want to.

193
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:18,920
He's being really strict with me right now.

194
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,200
Besides,

195
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:23,360
I feel like he's looking through me

196
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,440
at someone else.

197
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,920
Someone else?

198
00:08:28,960 --> 00:08:31,160
I think it's fine.

199
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,360
Sister,

200
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:37,320
if you're scared to go alone,

201
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,520
I'll go with you.

202
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,200
Well,

203
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,520
alright.

204
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:52,560
Yunyuan has been in seclusion more and more lately.

205
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,360
Oh,

206
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,920
it's fine.

207
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,200
There's no rush anyway.

208
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,640
We can ask him when he gets back.

209
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,160
Right?

210
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,760
Alright.

211
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:09,000
How can someone be so naive and silly?

212
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,560
How has she survived all these years?

213
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,160
Yinfeng,

214
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,400
why don't you go back first?

215
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,440
I'll wait here.

216
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:15,160
Okay.

217
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:17,520
I picked some fruit this morning.

218
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,920
I'll go make you some jam.

219
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:19,720
Great.

220
00:09:59,160 --> 00:09:59,880
Yunyuan,

221
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,640
you're back.

222
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,000
You're awake.

223
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,400
Why did you fall asleep out here?

224
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,200
I was waiting for you.

225
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,000
I fell asleep while waiting.

226
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:13,740
Don't wait for me outside from now on.

227
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,600
If you're tired, go sleep in your bed.

228
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,360
Do you hear me?

229
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,080
Okay.

230
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:19,840
Ah.

231
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:22,800
Here.

232
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:23,760
Yunyuan,

233
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,560
I'm really fully recovered.

234
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,320
Really.

235
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,320
Can I stop taking the medicine?

236
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,320
No.

237
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,000
You still need to take it.

238
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:31,760
Here.

239
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,240
Yunyuan.

240
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,000
After I finish this medicine,

241
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,520
can I go out and have fun tomorrow?

242
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,980
I'm really bored to death.

243
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,160
Be good, Ling'er.

244
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,160
Not tomorrow.

245
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,040
When I'm done being busy in a while,

246
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,680
I'll take you out then, okay?

247
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:52,680
No.

248
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:55,480
Why can I only go out if you accompany me?

249
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,000
We're just pretending to be together.

250
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,730
You can't restrict my freedom.

251
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,880
So, in your heart,

252
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,800
we are still just pretending.

253
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:08,960
Fine.

254
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,640
Very well.

255
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,520
Hey.

256
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,560
That's not what I meant. Don't go.

257
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,680
The barrier is weakest here.

258
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,180
Even if I can't open it,

259
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:37,000
my Spirit Pearl should be able to smash it open.

260
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,280
Where are you going?

261
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:47,920
Yunyuan.

262
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:50,360
How did you know I was going to sneak away?

263
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,680
I'm just being unreasonable.

264
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:52,720
I just feel wronged.

265
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,850
I just want to go out.

266
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,160
You can't go out.

267
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:57,450
No matter how much you fuss,

268
00:11:57,760 --> 00:12:00,320
I will never allow you to risk your safety.

269
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,880
How do you know what I'm thinking?

270
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,160
I don't know.

271
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:04,920
Hey.

272
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,120
You...

273
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:07,960
Let go of me.

274
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:08,920
I won't.

275
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,680
Put me down.

276
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,480
Yunyuan!

277
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,600
Just let me go out, please?

278
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,560
Pretty please.

279
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:20,360
Behave.

280
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:25,760
Yunyuan, why just won't you let me out?

281
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,010
Ling'er.

282
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,290
Listen to me.

283
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,360
I...

284
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:31,680
Yunyuan.

285
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:34,800
Yunyuan.

286
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,930
Why are you being like this?

287
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,200
Wait,

288
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,560
is he crazy?

289
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,880
